OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1780567570
OL,3,CTATA Steel workers jailed after tin
OL,4,Cworth #1.2m stolen from site
OL,6,FBetween July 2023 and September 2024,
OL,7,F48.8 tonnes of tin were stolen,
OL,8,Fequating to the value of #1.19m.
OL,10,FThe prosecution case outlined that the
OL,11,Fthefts took place on multiple
OL,12,Foccasions when a white ford transit
OL,13,Fvan driven by Membury was driven to
OL,14,Fthe TATA steel site. Membury was not
OL,15,Fan employee of the site.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1780567570
OL,3,CTATA Steel workers jailed after tin
OL,4,Cworth #1.2m stolen from site
OL,6,FThe court heard Stewart Jones was
OL,7,Femployed by TATA as a site security
OL,8,Fsupervisor and would provide access to
OL,9,FMembury to the Trostre site. He later
OL,10,Fcreated a false ID badge for Membury
OL,11,Funder the name David Davies which
OL,12,Fwould allow him to access the site
OL,13,Fhimself.
OL,15,FThomas Ashcroft was a casthouse
OL,16,Fsupervisor at the trostre site where
OL,17,Fhe would use his forklift to load the
OL,18,Finglots into Membury's van.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1780567570
OL,3,CTATA Steel workers jailed after tin
OL,4,Cworth #1.2m stolen from site
OL,6,FRichard Jones was an employee at TATA
OL,7,Fand assisted Ashcroft on an "ad-hoc"
OL,8,Fbasis to load the ingots into the van.
OL,9,FThe court heard Richard Jones was a
OL,10,Ftrusted TATA employee but not to the
OL,11,Fsame extent as the others.
