CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1780567570
OL,3,CTATA Steel workers jailed after tin
OL,4,Cworth #1.2m stolen from site
OL,6,FThe prosecution said that the thefts
OL,7,Fwere planned via a series of whatsapp
OL,8,Fmessages between the defendants as
OL,9,Fwell as face to face communication.
OL,10,FThe barrister then outlayed a series
OL,11,Fof these messages planning the thefts
OL,12,Fas well as interacting once funds had
OL,13,Fbeen paid to each of them.
OL,15,FThe court heard all of the defendants
OL,16,Fwere "conscious of the amount of money
OL,17,Fthey were making".
OL,26,@xD@FOUyD@QO]
