OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1780567570
OL,3,CTATA Steel workers jailed after tin
OL,4,Cworth #1.2m stolen from site
OL,6,FBetween July 2023 and September 2024
OL,7,FMembury received 68 deposits from
OL,8,Fvarious companies, equating to over
OL,9,F#743,826.
OL,11,FThe court heard he kept #339,770 of
OL,12,Fthis after distributing the rest to
OL,13,Fhis co-conspirators.
OL,15,FAshford received some #256,000 from
OL,16,FMembury, Stewart Jones #85,501 and
OL,17,FRichard Jones #61,97.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1780567570
OL,3,CTATA Steel workers jailed after tin
OL,4,Cworth #1.2m stolen from site
OL,6,FThe prosecution said that the
OL,7,Foperation came to an end on October
OL,8,F11, 2024 after police surveillance on
OL,9,Fthe site.
OL,11,FMembury was arrested after his van
OL,12,Fleft the Sessile Oak pub in Parc
OL,13,FPemberton at 5.30am and drove to the
OL,14,Fgates of the site where he used the
OL,15,Ffake company access pass. He was
OL,16,Farrested at 6am as he left the site.
OL,17,FThree swords were also found in the
OL,18,Fvan alongside the ingots.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1780567570
OL,3,CTATA Steel workers jailed after tin
OL,4,Cworth #1.2m stolen from site
OL,6,FAshford was arrested onsite the same
OL,7,Fmorning while the other two defendants
OL,8,Fwere arrested separately.
OL,10,FIn a statement from TATA, the court
OL,11,Fheard the thefts had a "significant
OL,12,Fand damaging impact on business" at
OL,13,Fthe Trostre site.
OL,15,FThey said they had spent "tens of
OL,16,Fthousands of pounds" strengthening
OL,17,Fsecurity controls.
OL,26,@sD@XOUtD@`O]wD@ZOUxD@TO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/14
