OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1780567570
OL,3,CTATA Steel workers jailed after tin
OL,4,Cworth #1.2m stolen from site
OL,6,FOn site parking is no longer permitted
OL,7,Fby employees on the site and the
OL,8,Fthefts had caused "long term trust
OL,9,Fissues with suppliers".
OL,11,FThe court heard all defendants had
OL,12,Fpreviously pleaded guilty to
OL,13,Fconspiracy to steal. Membury also
OL,14,Fpleaded guilty to possession of bladed
OL,15,Farticles linked to the swords found in
OL,16,Fthe van.
OL,18,FMembury is currently a serving
OL,19,Fprisoner and did not attend today's
OL,20,Fhearing. He will be sentenced at a
OL,21,Flater date.
OL,26,@pD@SOUqD@VO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/14
