OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1780567570
OL,3,CTATA Steel workers jailed after tin
OL,4,Cworth #1.2m stolen from site
OL,6,FIn his sentencing remarks Judge Paul
OL,7,FThomas KC described the thefts as of
OL,8,Fthe "most considerable scale" and a
OL,9,F"very sophisticated operation".
OL,11,FHe detailed how Membury was the
OL,12,F"biggest beneficiary" of the scheme.
OL,14,FHe said Ashford held a "vital role
OL,15,Fwithin TATA" though being a supervisor
OL,16,Fat the cast house and his crimes
OL,17,Famounted to a "gross breach of trust".
OL,26,@pD@EOUpD@]O]qD@AOUqD@^O]tD@AOUtD@UO]vD@
OL,26,AXOUwD@LO]yD@OOUyD@eO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1780567570
OL,3,CTATA Steel workers jailed after tin
OL,4,Cworth #1.2m stolen from site
OL,6,FRegarding Stewart Jones he said his
OL,7,Finvolvement given his role as a
OL,8,Fsecurity supervisor at the site
OL,9,Famounted to a "particular breach of
OL,10,Ftrust" and that the thefts "simply
OL,11,Fwould not have happened if you had not
OL,12,Fbeen involved".
OL,14,FThe court heard the stolen metal has
OL,15,Fnot been recovered and a proceeds of
OL,16,Fcrime investigation will be launched
OL,17,Flater this year.
OL,26,@qD@OOUrD@FO]rD@\OUtD@NO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G12/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1780567570
OL,3,CTATA Steel workers jailed after tin
OL,4,Cworth #1.2m stolen from site
OL,6,FAshford was sentenced to three years
OL,7,Fand four months in prison. Stewart
OL,8,FJones was sentenced to three years and
OL,9,Ffour months in prison. Richard Jones
OL,10,Fwas sentenced to 20 months in prison
OL,11,Fsuspended for two years. Membury will
OL,12,Fbe sentenced at a later date.
OL,14,FCraig Harding of the Crown Prosecution
OL,15,FService said: "This was a carefully
OL,16,Forchestrated operation which included
OL,17,Fthe use of a fake TATA ID pass.
OL,26,@wD@OOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G13/14
