OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46614
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1780567570
OL,3,CTATA Steel workers jailed after tin
OL,4,Cworth #1.2m stolen from site
OL,6,F"The criminality was a gross breach of
OL,7,Ftrust by those employed by the
OL,8,Fcompany, some of whom were in
OL,9,Fmanagerial or security positions. It
OL,10,Fcost the company more than #1m.
OL,12,F"The Crown Prosecution Service
OL,13,Fpresented strong evidence resulting in
OL,14,Fguilty pleas from all defendants, who
OL,15,Fhave now been brought to justice for
OL,16,Ftheir greed."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@MO]
